title: High End 32 Story High-Rise in Knox Neighborhood**Gas Range**
posting_body: A High-End Luxury High-Rise in the Knox Neighborhood with Panoramic Views of Uptown and the Katy Trail!
Walking Distance to Many Upscale Restaurants, Shopping, Night-Life, and Entertainment!
Each Apartment Has Several Desirable Amenities, Such as Quartz Countertops, Stainless Steel Appliances, a Gas Range Stove, Hardwood Floors, and Even a Built-In Wine Fridge!
Other Amenities Included; Spa Bathroom with a Stand-Up Shower and Oversized Soaking Tub, Walk-In Closet, Floor to Ceiling Windows, with a Full-Size Washer and Dryer Included.

These Beautiful Apartment Amenities Include a Luxurious Resort Lounge Pool with a Tanning Deck, a Wellness Center, a State of the Art Gym, and even a Pet Park for Your Beloved Animals, Plus So Much More.
These Luxury Apartments Even Include Climate Controlled Hallways, Parking Garage, Electric Vehicle Charging Stations, and Elevators, What More Could You Ask For?
Most Importantly They Have Great Management, 24 Hour Concierge, and Maintenance!!
